import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { useSelector } from "react-redux"; import axios from "axios"; import Moment from "react-moment"; import "./history.cards.css"; const HistoryCards = () => { const [userId, setUserId] = useState(""); const [userSummaries, setUserSummaries] = useState([]); const id = useSelector(state => state.userId); useEffect(() => { setUserId(id); axios .get("http://localhost:5000/summaries") .then(res => setUserSummaries(res.data)) .catch(err => console.log(err)); }, [id, userSummaries]); return (
    {userSummaries.reverse().map((summary, i) => summary.userId === userId ? (
  • {summary.date}
    {summary.mood}
    {summary.nicotine}
    {summary.meditation}
    {summary.excersice}
    {summary.hit_the_sack % 24}:00
    {summary.wake_up % 24}:00
    • ) : null )}
); }; export default HistoryCards;
